nodes.text: Dyshotto was a male Human who lived during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. He made his living as a merchant on board Carrick Station.
Dyshotto first appeared in Star Wars: The Old Republic, a video game released by BioWare in 2011, as a Coruscant planetary commendation vendor on board Carrick Station and on Coruscant itself.
